{"type": "article", "id": 4092, "title": "LV 概念家具系列", "description": "", "date": "2014-12-04T08:30:50Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 12, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605233400XfaNBQvMkUwH8oTt.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t去年年底的巴塞尔艺术展迈阿密海滩展会上，法国品牌 Louis Vuitton 搭出了法国女性建筑师 Charlotte Perriand 在 1934 年构建的作品「水上之屋」，今年同样是在迈阿密海滩展会上，Louis Vuitton 又带来了一组概念家具，设计灵感源自法国设计师 Pierre Paulin 与家具品牌 Herman Miller 的经典作品，扶手椅与沙发显出圆润柔和极具亲和力的轮廓，而书架、榻榻米与桌子等则更偏向层次分明与可调节的设计，少了一分奢侈品品牌的高冷，更加贴近于日常生活的实际使用需求。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233358XpGCoMJynPgeVrhR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052333598JTVqe03nzFLkapW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233359Pbvg7BCQFpeAdNKI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233400AuvxU25VDezw7EdB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}